# Installation of GHC 8.2.1

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution   
cd $HOME/Downloads  
wget http://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.2.1-rc3/ghc-8.2.0.20170704-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz


# This is a RELEASE candidate
mv ghc-8.2.0.20170704-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz ghc-8.2.1-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz


tar xvfJ ghc-8.2.1-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

# This is a RELEASE candidate
mv ghc-8.2.0.20170704 ghc-8.2.1

cd ghc-8.2.1 

# install  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-8.2.1  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-8.2.1  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd ..  
rm -rfv ghc-8.2.1*
~~~

